title: SF State co-hosts conference on the future of finance - SF State News
content: SF State co-hosts conference on the future of finance  SF State News
description: The Lam-Larsen FinTech Initiative at San Francisco State University is teaming up with the Federal Reserve Bank of San Francisco and the Center for Analytical Finance at the University of California at Santa Cruz to host a virtual conference that will give participants an in-depth look at the future of banking.
